      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the subframe has been structurally reinforced, and rod bearings were addressed preventatively using ACL shells. The double VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components for optimal cam phasing and throttle response. Chassis dynamics remain sharp with a factory M Variable Differential Lock and original suspension geometry. The exterior retains its factory deep-gloss finish with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin features immaculate Nappa leather with zero bolster wear. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
